  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to cargo-c</title>

    <para>
      The <application>cargo-c</application> package creates a cargo 
      subcommand to build and install C-ABI compatible dynamic and 
      static libraries.
    </para>

    &lfs122_checked;

